.DS_Store
*.log

# This repo is throughline's own public source, not a project consuming the
# plugin - the README's "Commit policy" (HANDOFF.md/logs/ should be committed,
# only buffer/ and .capture-errors are scratch) is guidance for consuming
# projects, not a rule for this repo. Here, all session data - however
# THROUGHLINE_DATA_DIR is configured - stays purely local; the maintainer's
# own dev notes aren't tracked in the public repo. Deliberate choice, not an
# oversight (a prior version of this file scoped only buffer/ and
# .capture-errors here too, which silently blocked committing this repo's own
# already-written HANDOFF.md - if that policy ever changes, narrow these back
# to match the README's documented pattern).
.claude/throughline/
.agent/handoff/
